  Phase 32 is documented in the HTML user manuals at
  Manual/Regalia-v1.0.8-manual-{zh,en}.html, Appendix A "版本更新日志" /
  "Version Changelog". Summary:

  Version: versionCode=108, versionName="1.0.8" (unchanged).

